B.HM=new A.bC(B.rZ,["Home","Projects","About","Contact","Hire me","Open to work","Flutter Developer | Web & Mobile Specialist","I build beautiful, performant applications with Flutter. Specialized in quality , stability and responsive design.","View Projects","Get in touch","ABOUT","Crafting Digital Experiences","Open to freelance","I'm a passionate Flutter developer with 2+ years of experience building production-grade applications. I specialize in creating beautiful user interfaces, managing complex state, and optimizing performance across platforms.","Core Skills","PROJECTS","Featured Work","Mobile applications built with Flutter \u2014 scalable, performant, and production-ready.","Quick View","Case Study","View More","CONTACT","Let's Work Together","Have a project in mind? Let's discuss how we can collaborate.","Email","Phone","LinkedIn","GitHub","Name","Email","Message","Send Message","Thank you! I'll get back to you soon.","Something went wrong. Please try again.","Name is required","Email is required","Please enter a valid email","Message is required","Your full name","your@email.com","Tell me about your project...","TECH STACK","Focus Areas","Current Goal","Freelance development \u2014 helping startups ship mobile products.","CURRENTLY BUILDING","What I'm Working On","Est. completion:","Progress","TESTIMONIALS","What Clients Say","Feedback from people I've worked with. (Sample testimonials \u2014 real reviews coming soon.)","\xa9 2024 Mental Warrior. All rights reserved.","Designed & Built with Flutter","CASE STUDY","Tech Stack","Problem","Solution","Tech Decisions","Challenges","Outcome","Smart Habit Tracker","A Flutter productivity app focused on habit formation with streak tracking, visual analytics, and smart reminders. Details coming soon.","Mental Warrior","A self-improvement app that helps users build a stronger, more disciplined mindset through structured daily habits, motivation tools, and personal growth tracking \u2014 all in one place.","People who want to improve themselves \u2014 students, young adults, anyone working on fitness, productivity, or mental well-being \u2014 feel unmotivated, overwhelmed, or stuck. They rely on multiple disconnected apps and struggle to stay consistent.","Built a unified self-improvement platform with structured daily habit tracking, mindset tools, and progress visibility. Offline-first with SQLite so the app works reliably without an internet connection, with a clear path to scale with Firebase sync.","Flutter chosen for cross-platform reach (Android + iOS) from a single codebase. SQLite used for fast, offline-first local storage ensuring the app works without connectivity. Architecture designed to be Firebase-ready for future cloud sync and user accounts.","The biggest challenge was designing a habit system that felt motivating rather than overwhelming \u2014 too many habits leads to burnout. Solved with a focused daily view and streak-based progress to keep users engaged without overloading them.","Live on Google Play Store with an active early-access tester community. Open source on GitHub. Available to the public via the Mental Warrior Testers group.","Aqua Track","A hydration tracking app built in just 3 days that adjusts your daily water goal based on your current climate, with a built-in intake calculator and smart reminders \u2014 making personalised hydration effortless.","Most people underdrink water without realising it, and generic 'drink 8 glasses' advice ignores real factors like heat, humidity, and activity level. Existing apps set the same fixed goal for everyone, leaving users with targets that don't fit their lifestyle.","Built a smart hydration tracker that uses the user's current climate data to dynamically adjust their daily water goal. A built-in intake calculator factors in body weight, activity, and temperature to give a personalised recommendation. One-tap logging and visual progress make it satisfying to stay on track.","Flutter for a smooth cross-platform experience. SQLite for lightweight offline-first local storage. Local notifications to send non-intrusive hydration reminders throughout the day.","The biggest challenge was building the climate-aware goal engine and intake calculator accurately within a 3-day timeline. Prioritised a clean, focused feature set and deferred non-essentials to ship a polished core experience fast.","Built and completed in 3 days. Currently in development for release on Google Play Store.","Incredible Flutter developer! Delivered our MVP on time with clean code and excellent communication throughout the whole project. Highly recommend.","Startup Founder","We hired this developer for a complex Flutter app with Firebase integration. The result exceeded expectations \u2014 clean UI and solid, scalable architecture.","Product Manager","Top-tier mobile developer. Great problem-solving skills and the ability to translate complex requirements into beautiful, functional apps.","Tech Lead","Loading...","Error","Try Again"],t.li)
B.HL=new A.bC(B.rZ,["Domov","Projekty","O mne","Kontakt","Kontaktuj ma","Otvoren\xfd pracovn\xfdm ponuk\xe1m","Flutter V\xfdvoj\xe1r | Web & Mobile \u0160pecialista","Vytv\xe1ram funk\u010dn\xe9 a v\xfdkonn\xe9 aplik\xe1cie s Flutter. \u0160pecializujem sa na kvalitu, stabilitu  a responz\xedvny dizajn.","Pozri Projekty","Kontaktuj ma","O MNE","Tvorba Digit\xe1lnych Produktov","Otvoren\xfd freelance ponuk\xe1m","Som v\xe1\u0161niv\xfd Flutter v\xfdvoj\xe1r s viac ako 2 rokmi sk\xfasenost\xed pri v\xfdvoji produk\u010dn\xfdch aplik\xe1ci\xed. \u0160pecializujem sa na vytv\xe1ranie kr\xe1snych pou\u017e\xedvate\u013esk\xfdch rozhran\xed, spr\xe1vu komplexn\xe9ho stavu a optimaliz\xe1ciu v\xfdkonu na v\u0161etk\xfdch platform\xe1ch.","K\u013e\xfa\u010dov\xe9 Zru\u010dnosti","PROJEKTY","Vybran\xe9 Projekty","Mobiln\xe9 aplik\xe1cie vytvoren\xe9 s Flutter \u2014 \u0161k\xe1lovate\u013en\xe9, v\xfdkonn\xe9 a pripraven\xe9 na produkciu.","R\xfdch\u013ea Prehliadka","Pr\xedpadov\xe1 \u0160t\xfadia","Zobrazi\u0165 Viac","KONTAKT","Po\u010fme Spolupracova\u0165","M\xe1te projekt na mysli?  Zistite , ako m\xf4\u017eeme spolupracova\u0165.","Email","Telef\xf3n","LinkedIn","GitHub","Meno","Email","Spr\xe1va","Posla\u0165 Spr\xe1vu","\u010eakujem! \u010coskoro sa v\xe1m oz\xfdvam.","Nie\u010do sa pokazilo. Pros\xedm, sk\xfaste znova.","Meno je povinn\xe9","Email je povinn\xfd","Zadajte pros\xedm platn\xfd email","Spr\xe1va je povinn\xe1","Va\u0161e cel\xe9 meno","vas@email.com","Povedzte mi o va\u0161om projekte...","TECH STACK","Oblasti z\xe1ujmu","Aktu\xe1lny cie\u013e","Freelance v\xfdvoj \u2014 pom\xe1ham startupom uv\xe1dza\u0165 mobiln\xe9 produkty na trh.","MOMENT\xc1LNE STAVIAM","Na \u010dom pracujem","Odh. dokon\u010denie:","Pokrok","REFERENCIE","\u010co hovoria klienti","Sp\xe4tn\xe1 v\xe4zba od \u013eud\xed, s ktor\xfdmi som pracoval. (Uk\xe1\u017ekov\xe9 referencie \u2014 skuto\u010dn\xe9 recenzie \u010doskoro.)","\xa9 2024 Mental Warrior. V\u0161etky pr\xe1va vyhraden\xe9.","Navrhnut\xe9 a Vytvoren\xe9 s Flutter","PR\xcdPADOV\xc1 \u0160T\xdaDIA","Tech Stack","Probl\xe9m","Rie\u0161enie","Technick\xe9 rozhodnutia","V\xfdzvy","V\xfdsledok","Smart Habit Tracker","Flutter aplik\xe1cia pre produktivitu zameran\xe1 na formovanie n\xe1vykov so sledovan\xedm s\xe9ri\xed, vizu\xe1lnou anal\xfdzou a inteligentn\xfdmi pripomienkami. Podrobnosti \u010doskoro.","Mental Warrior","Aplik\xe1cia pre sebarozvoj, ktor\xe1 pom\xe1ha pou\u017e\xedvate\u013eom budova\u0165 silnej\u0161iu a disciplinovanej\u0161iu myse\u013e prostredn\xedctvom \u0161trukt\xfarovan\xfdch denn\xfdch n\xe1vykov, motiva\u010dn\xfdch n\xe1strojov a sledovania osobn\xe9ho rastu \u2014 v\u0161etko na jednom mieste.","\u013dudia, ktor\xed chc\xfa zlep\u0161ova\u0165 seba \u2014 \u0161tudenti, mlad\xed dospel\xed, ka\u017ed\xfd pracuj\xfaci na kond\xedcii, produktivite alebo du\u0161evnom zdrav\xed \u2014 sa c\xedtia nemotivovane, zavalen\xed alebo uviaznut\xed. Spoliehaj\xfa sa na viacero nes\xfavisiacich aplik\xe1ci\xed a maj\xfa probl\xe9m zosta\u0165 konzistentn\xed.","Vybudovan\xe1 unifikovan\xe1 platforma pre sebarozvoj so \u0161trukt\xfarovan\xfdm denn\xfdm sledovan\xedm n\xe1vykov, n\xe1strojmi pre myse\u013e a vidite\u013enos\u0165ou pokroku. Offline-first s SQLite, tak\u017ee aplik\xe1cia funguje spo\u013eahlivo bez internetu, s jasnou cestou \u0161k\xe1lovania cez Firebase sync.","Flutter pre multiplatformn\xfd dosah (Android + iOS) z jedn\xe9ho k\xf3du. SQLite pre r\xfdchle offline-first ukladanie bez potreby konektivity. Architekt\xfara navrhnut\xe1 ako Firebase-ready pre bud\xfaci cloud sync a pou\u017e\xedvate\u013esk\xe9 \xfa\u010dty.","Najv\xe4\u010d\u0161ou v\xfdzvou bolo navrhn\xfa\u0165 syst\xe9m n\xe1vykov motivuj\xfaco, nie zdrvuj\xfaco \u2014 pr\xedli\u0161 ve\u013ea n\xe1vykov vedie k vyhoreniu. Vyrie\u0161en\xe9 cielen\xfdm denn\xfdm poh\u013eadom a pokrokom na z\xe1klade s\xe9ri\xed.","\u017div\xe9 na Google Play Store s akt\xedvnou komunitou testerov s pred\u010dasn\xfdm pr\xedstupom. Open source na GitHub. Dostupn\xe9 verejnosti cez skupinu Mental Warrior Testers.","Aqua Track","Aplik\xe1cia na sledovanie hydrat\xe1cie vytvoren\xe1 za 3 dni, ktor\xe1 prisp\xf4sobuje denn\xfd cie\u013e pr\xedjmu vody pod\u013ea v\xe1\u0161ho aktu\xe1lneho podnebia, so vstavanou kalkula\u010dkou a inteligentn\xfdmi pripomienkami \u2014 personalizovan\xe1 hydrat\xe1cia bez n\xe1mahy.","V\xe4\u010d\u0161ina \u013eud\xed pije nedostato\u010dne bez toho, aby si to uvedomila, a rada 'vypi 8 poh\xe1rov' ignoruje re\xe1lne faktory ako hor\xfa\u010dava, vlhkos\u0165 a aktivita. Existuj\xface aplik\xe1cie nastavuj\xfa rovnak\xfd cie\u013e pre v\u0161etk\xfdch.","Vytvoren\xfd inteligentn\xfd sledova\u010d hydrat\xe1cie vyu\u017e\xedvaj\xfaci klimatick\xe9 d\xe1ta na dynamick\xe9 prisp\xf4sobenie denn\xe9ho cie\u013ea. Kalkula\u010dka zoh\u013ead\u0148uje telesn\xfa hmotnos\u0165, aktivitu a teplotu. Jednodotykov\xe9 zaznamen\xe1vanie a vizu\xe1lny pokrok spr\xedjem\u0148uj\xfa dodr\u017eiavanie cie\u013ea.","Flutter pre plynul\xfd multiplatformn\xfd z\xe1\u017eitok. SQLite pre \u013eahk\xe9 offline-first ukladanie. Lok\xe1lne notifik\xe1cie pre nen\xe1siln\xe9 pripomienky hydrat\xe1cie po\u010das d\u0148a.","Najv\xe4\u010d\u0161ou v\xfdzvou bolo presne vybudova\u0165 engine cie\u013eov z\xe1visl\xfdch od podnebia a kalkula\u010dku v r\xe1mci 3-d\u0148ov\xe9ho \u010dasov\xe9ho r\xe1mca. Prioritizovan\xe1 \u010dist\xe1, s\xfastreden\xe1 sada funkci\xed.","Vytvoren\xe9 a dokon\u010den\xe9 za 3 dni. Moment\xe1lne vo v\xfdvoji pre vydanie na Google Play Store.","Neuverite\u013en\xfd Flutter v\xfdvoj\xe1r! Doru\u010dil na\u0161e MVP v\u010das s \u010dist\xfdm k\xf3dom a v\xfdbornou komunik\xe1ciou po\u010das cel\xe9ho projektu. Vrelo odpor\xfa\u010dam.","Zakladate\u013e startupu","Najali sme tohto v\xfdvoj\xe1ra na komplexn\xfa Flutter aplik\xe1ciu s Firebase integr\xe1ciou. V\xfdsledok prekonal o\u010dak\xe1vania \u2014 \u010dist\xe9 UI a sol\xeddna, \u0161k\xe1lovate\u013en\xe1 architekt\xfara.","Product Manager","\u0160pi\u010dkov\xfd mobiln\xfd v\xfdvoj\xe1r. V\xfdborn\xe9 schopnosti rie\u0161enia probl\xe9mov a schopnos\u0165 prelo\u017ei\u0165 zlo\u017eit\xe9 po\u017eiadavky do kr\xe1snych, funk\u010dn\xfdch aplik\xe1ci\xed.","Tech Lead","Na\u010d\xedtava sa...","Chyba","Sk\xfaste znova"],t.li)
